      "description": "Validation against FDA generic centrifugal blood pump experimental hemolysis data across 5 adult normothermic operating points (flow 2.4–6.0 L/min, speed 2400–3600 RPM). RH index predicted within 12% of experimental values at all points. Dataset collected and validation completed in March 2023, prior to the Q4 2025 envelope expansion to pediatric and low-flow conditions.",
