      "rationale": "Experimental conditions (blood analog fluid viscosity, hematocrit 35–40%, temperature 37°C, adult flow rates 2.4–6.0 L/min) were well-controlled and documented. Conditions match the pre-expansion COU. Pediatric and low-flow conditions (cardiac index 1.8–2.8 L/min/m², flow 0.5–1.5 L/min) added to the COU in Q4 2025 were not represented in any experimental test campaign."
