      "rationale": "NIH and RH index are the regulatory-accepted QoIs for hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance. Shear stress scalar transport model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger power law) directly maps to these QoIs. Relevance is maintained for the original COU; applicability to pediatric low-flow shear regimes has not been verified."
