      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities cover the COU operating envelope with sufficient fidelity to support the credibility claim.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities conducted in 2022–2023 covered the adult normothermic CPB operating envelope (flow 2.4–6.0 L/min, speed 2400–3600 RPM) that constituted the original COU. The COU was subsequently expanded in Q4 2025 to include pediatric patients and low-flow assist conditions. No additional validation activities have been conducted or linked to address this expanded envelope. Re-validation is described as planned for H1 2026. The achieved level of 2 reflects the pre-expansion validation coverage only; the gap introduced by the envelope expansion is not resolved by any linked evidence.",
